        <updated>2022-06-14T20:26:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[More breaking changes.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>More breaking changes.</p><p>I finally got round to documenting the hooks. As I often find with attempting
to explain something, the process reveals things that need improvement.</p><p>This ended in me renaming the interaction hooks to: <code>useDrag</code>, <code>useZoom</code>, and
<code>useClick</code>, which I find more obvious.</p><p>I think the next step is to come out of alpha versions and make a major release.</p><p>Rob</p>]]></content>
